node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alan Semsar 🛩 in Mohegan Sun Casino Las Vegas with @virginhotelslv, @virginhotels, and @mohegansunlasvegas. May be an image of 1 person, drink and indoor.

node.text: The Heat high roller lounge baby that’s the smile of winning 💰💰💵💵 Mo Money Mo Money #winnerwinnerchickendinner #TheShah thank you @virginhotels for a week of VIP treatment truly spoiled by your #YES service and huge thanks to @mohegansunlasvegas nothing like winning in a casino 🎰 💳💵💎 #labordayweekend #laborday @virginhotels

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alan Semsar 🛩 in Shag room with @virginhotelslv, @virginhotels, and @mohegansunlasvegas. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: Shall we Shag now or shag later?! #OhBehave love this place the perfect getaway from everything #TheShah thank you @virginhotelslv for the VIP treatment again #ShagRoom #Yes
Check out the gorgeous line up of Maserati’s new cars #trofeo and the upcoming MC20 @maserati @maseratiusa at Maserati of Newport Beach @maseratiofnewportbeach #TheArtOfFast

40 plus days left to the Las Vegas Food & Wine Festival presented by United Airlines @united grab a ticket 🎟 and help us donate to @criticalcarecomics @shadetreevegas because it feels sooooo good to give.  #VegasVibes
